nodes.text: Empire's Station I was a space station in the Karthakk system belonging to the Galactic Empire during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

Empire's Station I was a location in Jump to Lightspeed, the 2004 expansion pack for the massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, prior to the game's closure on December 15, 2011.
